Build:
-----

You need the the KDE SC4.4 libraries and CMake to build this plasmoid.

# cmake .
# make

As root:

# make install

or as a sudoer:

# sudo make install

And finally,

# kbuildsycoca4
# kquitapp plasma-desktop (or kquitapp plasma-netbook)
# plasma-desktop (or plasma-netbook)



